  "text": "It has been observed that the through-thickness elastic modulus of GFPP used in this work is strain rate dependent. A through-thickness elastic modulus of 4.8 GPa used was extracted from an experiment under a strain rate of 10 3 s −1 , while the static through-thickness elastic modulus was found to be half of the measured value under such strain rate. However, E 1 and E 2 for GFPP were observed to be strain rate independent [CITATION_1] .",
